snippet.title: Super Real Fishing (スーパーリアルフィシング) (Game Boy Color)
snippet.description: This is also another Rumble Pak game from my friend's list. By Bottom Up (also known for games like Granduel) ^^ and Sky Fishing 753, Perfect Fishing. Part of the music while about to go fishing sounds like one of the melodies from Super Mario Bros. 3.
